      "repair_reason": "Automation is paused with human-review/protected maintainer handling, and the remaining blockers are security-sensitive policy plus CI failures that need maintainer review.; Needs attention: The diff still leaves direct loopback paths where the new managed-proxy policy says traffic should be proxied or limited to the configured Gateway URL.; Review finding: [P1] Carry the configured target into the client — src/gate... (sha=5df4e9a57b5315733e8b5296404460b98f382508)",
